data.description: Welcome to your dream waterfront oasis in the best neighborhood in the world, Riviera Bay! Nestled along the Grand Canal, this exquisite home offers an unparalleled lifestyle of elegance and comfort. Step inside to discover a meticulously designed open floor plan that seamlessly blends modern sophistication with the charm of waterfront living. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. Boasting three bedrooms and two bathrooms, including a luxurious master suite, this home provides ample space for family and guests. Each room is thoughtfully appointed with upscale finishes and attention to detail, ensuring both style and functionality. Prepare to be amazed by the gourmet kitchen, complete with top-of-the-line appliances, sleek countertops, and custom cabinetry. Whether you're whipping up a quick breakfast or hosting a lavish dinner party, this culinary haven is sure to impress even the most discerning chef. Step outside to your private oasis and behold the breathtaking views of the Grand Canal. Enjoy morning coffee or evening cocktails on your expansive patio as you soak in the mesmerizing sight of vibrant sunrises and dazzling sunsets over the water. This home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also boasts practical features such as a two-car garage, providing ample space for parking and storage. A new seawall and new dock with lift ensure worry-free waterfront living for years to come.  Indulge in the ultimate waterfront lifestyle in Riviera Bay, where every day feels like a vacation. Whether you're boating, fishing, or simply relaxing by the water's edge, this home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and natural beauty. A neighborhood that is a way of life with so many traditions such as the Christmas Eve Boat Parade, golf cart parades, lining the streets with American Flags and luminaries, yard sales, socials, with two parks, a community boat ramp, and a gorgeous butterfly garden!  Catch the local's saying, "It's Always a Great Day in Riviera Bay!!
